OL,6,FBut it says public and private bodies
OL,7,F"engage in performative actions and
OL,8,Fevents without genuinely addressing
OL,9,Ftangible issues faced by women."
OL,11,FInternational Women's Day celebrates
OL,12,Fthe social, economic, cultural, and
OL,13,Fpolitical achievements of women and
OL,14,Fmarks a call to action for
OL,15,Faccelerating women's equality.
OL,17,FEvents have taken place around the
OL,18,Fglobe, including many in the UK.
